NAME User Enumeration
DESCRIPTION Enumerate common user directories using FOR loop
CATEGORY recon
PLATFORMS WIN
PLATFORM WIN
DELAY 500
OPEN_POWERSHELL
PRINT Enumerating users...
LED_COLOR CYAN
STRINGLN Get-ChildItem C:\Users | ForEach-Object { Write-Host $_.Name }
DELAY 2000
REM Check common service accounts
FOR $I = 1 TO 5
  STRINGLN echo Checking batch $I of common accounts...
  DELAY 500
END_FOR
STRINGLN net user
DELAY 3000
LED_COLOR GREEN
PRINT Enumeration complete
